{"article_id":"c6RbYdqtRfHGzTtl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"New Jersey Gov . Chris Christie poured everything","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"he had","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"into New Hampshire ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"clawing his way up the polls in a crowded field and Donald Trump-dominated year","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"while tainted by scandal back home .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"In the last few weeks before Tuesday 's primary , and under fire from Rubio and his super PACs , Christie became pre-occupied with the Florida senator .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Christie 's criticism of the candidate grew increasingly sharp behind closed doors ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"according to people familiar with the conversations .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"He would see a Rubio interview","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"or read a story","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"featuring Rubio","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"and complain to staff or supporters","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"that he simply did not see the appeal .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"He listened to Rubio provide canned quotes in each debate","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"when attacked ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"refuse to look Christie in the eye during his response ,","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"Christie told people .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"It was a sign of weakness","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"-- and a sign of a weak candidate --","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"in his view .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"By Saturday night in Goffstown , New Hampshire , after Rubio 's surprising third-place finish in Iowa , everyone knew what was coming ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Rubio included .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"`` Marco , the thing is this , ''","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Christie said at the ABC debate at St. Anselm 's College .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"`` When you 're president of the United States ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"when you 're a governor of a state ,","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"the memorized 30-second speech","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"where you talk about how great America is at the end of it","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"does n't solve one problem for one person . ''","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Asked the next day","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"how Rubio could 've missed what was coming ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"Christie resorted to `` the great political philosopher Mike Tyson , '' the famous former world heavyweight-boxing champion .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"`` Everyone has a plan","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"until they get punched in the face , ''","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"Christie told reporters .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"Christie , after all , had been getting punched in the face for two years .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"He could now take credit","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"for wounding a candidate","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"he and his team viewed as unprepared for the job .","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"But that would be the extent of his accomplishments in New Hampshire .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Tuesday night , he received his own knockout blow ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"finishing sixth in New Hampshire .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Wednesday , he threw in the towel","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"`` I ran for president","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"to say","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that the government needs to once again work for the people ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"not the people work for the government .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"while running for president","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"I tried to reinforce what I have always believed","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"--","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"that speaking your mind matters ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"that experience matters ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"that competence matters","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"and that it will always matter","depth":15},{"id":57,"text":"in leading our nation , ''","depth":15},{"id":58,"text":"Christie wrote in a Facebook post .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"`` That message was heard by and stood for by a lot of people ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"but just not enough","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"and that 's OK . ''","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"The story of Christie 's rise and fall in the state","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"where he pinned all of his hopes","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"is based on interviews with more than a dozen of his advisers , donors , fundraisers , supporters and rival campaign aides .","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"In the end , Christie could not get past both his own personal baggage and his status as another governor of a moderate or blue state","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"selling his personal appeal during a general election campaign to a Republican base","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"clearly looking for new blood .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Once considered a front-runner in the 2016 sweepstakes ,","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"a litany of policy decisions back home in New Jersey ,","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"combined with the federal investigation into a politically driven bridge closing","depth":16},{"id":71,"text":"crafted by his staff in the governor 's office ,","depth":16},{"id":72,"text":"had marred his hopes","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"-- so much so that many top Republicans wondered","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"whether a run was worth it at all .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"And in a race","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"dominated by GOP outsiders like Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"a governor","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"touting his experience , a la Jeb Bush , Rick Perry , John Kasich and George Pataki ,","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"was n't a strong sell .","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"Christie announced his candidacy","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"knowing full well","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"that he had a lot of ground","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"to make up .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"With a group of top-tier advisers , he went to work early crafting a strategy","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"to vault himself back into the GOP top tier .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"That plan revolved around New Hampshire ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"following the tradition of the state 's successful candidates :","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"come often ,","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"work hard ,","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"shower the state 's politicians with attention","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"( or , in Christie 's case , never-ending text messages )","depth":16},{"id":92,"text":"and the rest will take care of itself .","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"He would spend more than 70 days in the state ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"holding 160 events and 60 town halls .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"But","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"as the months moved along","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"and Donald Trump upended every campaign 's initial plans ,","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"the topline strategy inside Christie 's team evolved into a multi-part bank shot","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"-- one","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"that","depth":16},{"id":101,"text":"even they would admit","depth":16},{"id":102,"text":"needed breaks","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"to succeed .","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"On paper , it was perfect :","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"First , Christie would use his deep connections to popular Iowa Gov . Terry Branstad","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"to harness a better-than-terrible showing in Iowa .","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"Then , he would go back to New Hampshire ,","depth":16},{"id":108,"text":"where his campaign and its supporting super PAC had invested a majority of their resources in on-the-the ground work and television advertising","depth":17},{"id":109,"text":"to turn flagging favorability ratings upside down .","depth":17},{"id":110,"text":"Finally , he 'd have a big debate night ,","depth":16},{"id":111,"text":"and close the deal with the historically","depth":18},{"id":112,"text":"( and frustratingly )","depth":18},{"id":113,"text":"late-deciding voters in the state .","depth":17},{"id":114,"text":"A strong showing Tuesday would then open the doors to their extensive supporter and donor networks","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"-- - a deep-pocketed group","depth":16},{"id":116,"text":"wary of sending a first-term senator like Rubio to the White House .","depth":16},{"id":117,"text":"As the chairman of the Republican Governors Association in 2014 , Christie helped elect seven new GOP governors","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"and divvied up extensive financial resources","depth":15},{"id":119,"text":"-- to the tune of $ 100 million --","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"to help 17 others gain re-election .","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"Prove his viability","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"and those investments in time and money would come home ,","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"his advisers predicted .","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"By mid-January , it all seemed to be working .","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"Christie 's approval ratings had jumped as many as 20 points in Granite State polls .","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"His town halls became events in themselves","depth":16},{"id":127,"text":"-- each bigger than the next .","depth":16},{"id":128,"text":"His campaign and supporting super PAC saw the events register so well","depth":16},{"id":129,"text":"that they became the basis of many of their television ads","depth":17},{"id":130,"text":"-- a straight-talking governor with real experience ,","depth":18},{"id":131,"text":"who had notched a sweeping re-election victory in a traditionally Democrat-leaning state .","depth":18},{"id":132,"text":"David Sacks , an independent voter from Hollis , vividly remembered his first interaction with Christie at a friend 's house .","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"`` He grabbed me immediately , ''","depth":17},{"id":134,"text":"Sacks said .","depth":17},{"id":135,"text":"He left the event","depth":17},{"id":136,"text":"saying to himself ,","depth":19},{"id":137,"text":"`` Man , this is the guy , ''","depth":20},{"id":138,"text":"he recalled .","depth":20},{"id":139,"text":"`` Why not Christie ? ''","depth":18},{"id":140,"text":"But the liabilities never dissipated .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"New Jersey 's economy ,","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"while on the upswing in recent months ,","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"had been bleak for much of Christie 's tenure .","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"Opposition research ,","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"shared with CNN from multiple campaigns ,","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"was extensive on areas","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"where Christie allegedly took positions","depth":15},{"id":148,"text":"that broke with Republican orthodoxy .","depth":15},{"id":149,"text":"One aide in a rival campaign put it succinctly :","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"`` We all saw his rise","depth":16},{"id":151,"text":"-- it was very real --","depth":16},{"id":152,"text":"but we were never worried .","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"We knew","depth":15},{"id":154,"text":"a week of negative ads would bring him back down to earth","depth":16},{"id":155,"text":"whenever we wanted . ''","depth":16},{"id":156,"text":"Super PACs","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"supporting Bush , Rubio and Kasich","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"unloaded on Christie ,","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"attacking him on his state 's acceptance of Common Core on education , the Bridge-gate scandal and past statements on gun control and abortion .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"Rubio himself started reading , theatrically from a piece of paper","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"pulled from his pocket ,","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"Christie 's press release","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"that appeared to make it look like he supported President Barack Obama 's Supreme Court nomination of Sonia Sotomayor .","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"Within weeks , Christie 's favorability ratings nose-dived","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"and so did his poll numbers .","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"Meanwhile , Christie 's financial picture continued to worsen .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"He closed 2015 with a little more than $ 1 million","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"to spend .","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"While money was still coming in","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"-- a series of fundraisers in January brought in seven figures ,","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"according to two people familiar with the process --","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"it was n't nearly enough","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"to challenge the seemingly endless attacks","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"that were coming his way .","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"His foray into Iowa fell flat , even with the extensive Branstad connections and two campaign stops with the governor himself .","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"He logged the 2 %","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"he 'd been polling at for months","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"and in the process , frustrated donors","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"by undertaking a six-day swing through Iowa","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"-- - time","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"that could have been spent","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"working relatively unopposed in New Hampshire .","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"Days before New Hampshire voters went to the polls ,","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"Christie was struggling to stay in the conversation ,","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"falling into the mid-single digits","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"and struggling to rediscover the message","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"that connected .","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"From that , the plan became :","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"attack Rubio .","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"The initial attack was always in the plans ,","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"but just how personal it got was not ,","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"according to aides .","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"During the drive to his New Hampshire campaign headquarters in Bedford , he made clear","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"while he was resolved to launch his first salvo ,","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"he would stay away from personal attacks .","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"At an arranged meeting with reporters","depth":15},{"id":198,"text":"after he greeted volunteers ,","depth":15},{"id":199,"text":"he almost succeeded .","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"He started","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"by saying","depth":16},{"id":202,"text":"it would be an `` interesting week '' for Rubio","depth":16},{"id":203,"text":"and went through his practiced lines about the dangers of first term senators .","depth":14},{"id":204,"text":"But","depth":15},{"id":205,"text":"as the question and answer session was about to end ,","depth":16},{"id":206,"text":"something clicked in Christie .","depth":16},{"id":207,"text":"He proceeded to launch into a three-minute personal indictment of Rubio 's lack of political talent , reliance on advisers , inability","depth":17},{"id":208,"text":"to do retail politics","depth":17},{"id":209,"text":"and general lack of life accomplishment .","depth":16},{"id":210,"text":"He punctuated each attack line with a new nickname for Rubio :","depth":16},{"id":211,"text":"`` the boy in the bubble . ''","depth":16},{"id":212,"text":"The backstory is both strategic and personal for Christie .","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"Rubio came out of Iowa with the wind at his back","depth":13},{"id":214,"text":"-- so much so that members of Christie 's team received calls from certain party stalwarts","depth":14},{"id":215,"text":"that appeared to hint","depth":15},{"id":216,"text":"that it was time","depth":16},{"id":217,"text":"for Christie to drop out","depth":17},{"id":218,"text":"and the party to coalesce around Rubio .","depth":17},{"id":219,"text":"Christie ,","depth":16},{"id":220,"text":"who had been swiping at Rubio for weeks in town halls ,","depth":16},{"id":221,"text":"wanted to cut off the Florida senator 's rise","depth":15},{"id":222,"text":"before supporters and , more importantly , donors started to flee .","depth":14},{"id":223,"text":"Christie had a good idea","depth":16},{"id":224,"text":"that he 'd pulled off what he pledged to do at Saturday night 's debate ,","depth":16},{"id":225,"text":"but he was n't sure .","depth":15},{"id":226,"text":"It was none other than Donald Trump","depth":17},{"id":227,"text":"who confirmed","depth":18},{"id":228,"text":"what Christie thought during the first commercial break .","depth":18},{"id":229,"text":"`` Wow .","depth":19},{"id":230,"text":"That was tremendous , ''","depth":19},{"id":231,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":19},{"id":232,"text":"grabbing Christie 's arm ,","depth":19},{"id":233,"text":"according to a source familiar with the exchange .","depth":17},{"id":234,"text":"His next stop was a check-in with his wife , Mary Pat ,","depth":17},{"id":235,"text":"standing off the stage .","depth":17},{"id":236,"text":"She echoed Trump 's analysis .","depth":16},{"id":237,"text":"The 72 hours","depth":13},{"id":238,"text":"that followed","depth":13},{"id":239,"text":"comprised of part victory lap","depth":13},{"id":240,"text":"-- - it was clear Christie had frozen the post-Iowa rush of donors and supporters to Rubio --","depth":13},{"id":241,"text":"and part urgent campaign push","depth":12},{"id":242,"text":"to lock in the voters","depth":13},{"id":243,"text":"falling away from the senator .","depth":13},{"id":244,"text":"The campaign 's internal polling showed a consistent uptick in Christie 's numbers ,","depth":8},{"id":245,"text":"but more and more , things were shifting toward Bush and among , undeclared voters , Kasich .","depth":8},{"id":246,"text":"While Christie did the work","depth":9},{"id":247,"text":"everyone in the race was hoping for ,","depth":9},{"id":248,"text":"it increasingly looked like he would n't be the candidate","depth":9},{"id":249,"text":"to benefit .","depth":9},{"id":250,"text":"JUST WATCHED Gov . Chris Christie on State of the Union :","depth":6},{"id":251,"text":"Full Interview Replay","depth":6},{"id":252,"text":"More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":253,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":254,"text":"Gov . Chris Christie on State of the Union :","depth":8},{"id":255,"text":"Full Interview 04:55","depth":8},{"id":256,"text":"Christie was convinced after Saturday","depth":9},{"id":257,"text":"that the race had been flipped on its head","depth":10},{"id":258,"text":"-- no longer was finishing first among governors the metric .","depth":10},{"id":259,"text":"Instead , it was survive","depth":10},{"id":260,"text":"and advance ,","depth":10},{"id":261,"text":"get to the next debate","depth":10},{"id":262,"text":"and try for another big moment .","depth":10},{"id":263,"text":"Then CBS News released its criteria","depth":9},{"id":264,"text":"to qualify for the next debate .","depth":9},{"id":265,"text":"Only the top five in New Hampshire would move forward .","depth":8},{"id":266,"text":"By 10 p.m. on primary night , it became clear Christie would do no better than sixth .","depth":7},{"id":267,"text":"As Christie walked to the podium in the ballroom at a Radisson hotel in Nashua ,","depth":10},{"id":268,"text":"he remained convinced","depth":12},{"id":269,"text":"that he had connected with the people in the state","depth":12},{"id":270,"text":"-- and appeared to be genuinely surprised","depth":12},{"id":271,"text":"he did n't do better .","depth":12},{"id":272,"text":"It had become clear to him and his team that people had gravitated to his message .","depth":9},{"id":273,"text":"`` I have both won elections","depth":12},{"id":274,"text":"that I was supposed to lose","depth":12},{"id":275,"text":"and I have lost elections","depth":12},{"id":276,"text":"that I was supposed to win , ''","depth":12},{"id":277,"text":"Christie said .","depth":10},{"id":278,"text":"`` And what that means is you never know ,","depth":10},{"id":279,"text":"and it 's both the magic and mystery of politics","depth":11},{"id":280,"text":"that you never quite know","depth":13},{"id":281,"text":"when which is going to happen","depth":13},{"id":282,"text":"even when you think","depth":13},{"id":283,"text":"you do . ''","depth":13},{"id":284,"text":"For weeks","depth":7},{"id":285,"text":"as primary day approached ,","depth":8},{"id":286,"text":"Christie would close his town halls with a story from one of his first events in the state .","depth":8},{"id":287,"text":"As Christie told it ,","depth":9},{"id":288,"text":"he was approached by an elderly man","depth":10},{"id":289,"text":"after he wrapped up .","depth":10},{"id":290,"text":"The man was effusive in his praise for Christie .","depth":11},{"id":291,"text":"He liked what he had to say ,","depth":12},{"id":292,"text":"he liked his positions","depth":13},{"id":293,"text":"and overall he was ready to vote for him .","depth":13},{"id":294,"text":"But he would n't ,","depth":11},{"id":295,"text":"the man told Christie .","depth":11},{"id":296,"text":"Then he turned","depth":10},{"id":297,"text":"to walk away .","depth":10},{"id":298,"text":"`` Wait -- sir , tell me what I did ? ''","depth":9},{"id":299,"text":"Christie would recount to the chuckling audience .","depth":9},{"id":300,"text":"The man turned around slowly","depth":10},{"id":301,"text":"and informed Christie","depth":11},{"id":302,"text":"he had n't done one crucial thing :","depth":12},{"id":303,"text":"ask for the man 's vote .","depth":12},{"id":304,"text":"Christie quickly did just that .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":609,"left":0,"right":608,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":608,"left":365,"right":607,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":365,"left":309,"right":364,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":307,"right":308,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":307,"left":306,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":306,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":364,"left":324,"right":363,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":324,"left":6,"right":323,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":323,"left":310,"right":322,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":322,"left":314,"right":321,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":314,"left":312,"right":313,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":312,"left":9,"right":311,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":311,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":313,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":321,"left":318,"right":320,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":318,"left":14,"right":317,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":317,"left":316,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":316,"left":15,"right":315,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":315,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":320,"left":319,"right":21,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":319,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":363,"left":345,"right":362,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":345,"left":325,"right":344,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":325,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":344,"left":342,"right":343,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":342,"left":341,"right":41,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":341,"